        "TileImage": "$($repository ebd039a9-8327-436e-bbcb-738378b95430).Image",
        "Description": "Good afternoon, 47. With Kieran Simmons eliminated, the only member of Operation Skyfall left is their leader. Unfortunately, we still don&apos;t know where they are, so we&apos;ll be sending you undercover to find out.\r\rAlright, 47. Your destination is the Milton Fitzpatrick bank in New York. After some digging, we found out that the leader has an account there. But it&apos;s encrypted. Thankfully, there are two men in the bank who have access to the data. You must take them out.\r\rGood luck, 47.",
